## Auto-Sync Events Table

| Event | products updated | inventories updated | orders updated |
|-------|-----------------|--------------------|-|
| Admin adds product | ✅ Created | ✅ Created (INITIAL) | — |
| Admin edits product | ✅ Updated | ✅ Updated (ADMIN_UPDATE or RESTOCK) | — |
| Admin deletes product | ✅ Deleted | ✅ Deleted automatically | — |
| Admin edits inventory qty | ✅ Synced | ✅ Updated (RESTOCK/ADMIN_UPDATE) | — |
| Customer buys product | ✅ Stock decremented | ✅ Updated (SALE, with orderId) | ✅ Created |
| Customer buys multiple items | ✅ All products decremented | ✅ All inventories updated | ✅ 1 order with all items |

