## Payment Methods

The 5 supported Pakistan payment methods are validated at the schema level:

```
COD           — Cash on Delivery
ATM Card      — Debit/Credit card payment
Bank Transfer — Direct bank transfer
Easypaisa     — Mobile wallet
JazzCash      — Mobile wallet
```

Any other value will return a `400 Validation failed` error.

