## How to Add `selectedColor` to Cart

Currently when a customer clicks "Add to Cart" on a product, the `selectedColor` defaults to `''`.
To capture it, update `ProductCard.jsx` `handleAddToCart` to also pass `activeColor`:

```jsx
// In ProductCard.jsx, update handleAddToCart:
const handleAddToCart = (e) => {
  e.stopPropagation();
  // ... existing size logic ...
  addToCart({
    ...product,
    selectedSize:  product.sizes?.[0] ?? '',   // or your current logic
    selectedColor: activeColor ?? '',           // ← add this line
  });
};
```

The `activeColor` state already exists in ProductCard — it just wasn't being passed to the cart.